MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: apps/client/src/.+/(popover|sheet|picker|overlay|modal|drawer|reveal|menu).*\.tsx?$|apps/client/src/.+/.*(Popover|Sheet|Picker|Overlay|Modal|Drawer|Reveal|Menu|Bar).tsx?$
ADVISORY: |
  CSS z-index gotcha that broke CommandPicker clicks in the Pulse shell:

  z-index has NO EFFECT on `position: static` (default) elements. Setting
  `zIndex: 40` on a div without a `position` value silently does nothing.

  When you have a `position: fixed` backdrop AND inline-flow content that
  should appear above it, the static content's z-index is ignored — the
  backdrop captures all clicks even though it's visually behind.

  Wrong (cards unclickable, backdrop intercepts clicks):
    <div onClick={onClose} style={{ position:'fixed', inset:0, zIndex:39 }} />
    <motion.div style={{ display:'flex', zIndex:40 }}>
      <button>...</button>  ← click goes to the backdrop
    </motion.div>

  Right:
    <motion.div style={{ position:'relative', display:'flex', zIndex:40 }}>

  Rule: any element with `zIndex` MUST also have `position: relative|absolute|fixed|sticky`.
